stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Accumulating
    Accumulating --> Processing: batch_size reached (20)
    Accumulating --> Processing: timeout reached (2s)
    Processing --> Accumulating: batch processed
    Processing --> [*]: shutdown
    
